data.description: Up front River Plantation, NEVER FLOODED! Unique entry w/ floor to high ceiling brick wall that continues to family room w/distinctive fireplace & wet bar in one of a kind living area. Modern touches add character to this charming home. Dining+breakfast area. All bedrooms have walkin closets. Primary + 5th bdrm/office down. 3 bdrms up, all connect to a bathroom. Black slat sliding doors. Sunroom up offers great views, perfect area for holiday displays. Tons of WOW 2020 upgrades: kitchen cabinets/fixtures/faucets/SS appl/black granite counters/wood laminate floors/tile bathrooms/unique backsplash & light fixtures/solid surface counters in baths/carpet up/dbl pane windows/Levolor blinds/electrical box/water heater/roof w/ 30yr transferable warranty, WOW! 2022 replaced attic duct work. 4 car garage+addtl parking. Wrought iron fence/gated driveway to spacious wood fenced back yard w/deck & plenty of room for outdoor activity. Convenient to shopping/dining/medical facilities/entertainment.
